originalText.text: Got a top tailored here, they took in the straps and tailored the sides which were too big. They did a good job, I’m happy with the result and will bring more smaller alterations jobs here. Will update this review once I get more items tailored. Price was reasonable too.

originalText.text: I’ve done 2 alterations and they did both at a very reasonable price. Both turned out excellent! They’re my trusted cleaners. Friendly service too - thanks D!

originalText.text: They ruined my shirts and there's not even a sorry. Don't come here if your shirt has shell bottom on it. They would break the bottoms and won't even say a sorry. They will blame that everything is your fault because they wrote it in the disclaimer in the receipt, which is given to me after my purchase. They won't try to notice you that the bottom is dangerous and subject to cracking. I had my shirt cleaned in other stores various time and that never happened. Finally they replaced my cracked bottoms with unmatching ones. Horrible service, horrible attitude.

originalText.text: I dropped off a black sequined top and a large wool sweater -- both were beautifully cleaned at a reasonable price, and the woman at the counter was very nice, remembered my name (which was good since I lost the piece of paper). She didn't need it because she not only remembered my name, she knew exactly where my items were. And it was my first time there.  I'll be back!
